name: I NEED A JOB - the editions

metadata.name: I NEED A JOB
metadata.description:
I NEED A JOB is the first piece I ever planted onto a blockchain. First came the music video - minted on Ethereum. It sold for 8.8ETH to a group of 47 people who combined resources to buy it. I decided to give these editions to those people for free as a token of appreciation for validating my request to be considered a professional creative. 

If you end up holding this - I hope you see it as a reminder that there is something you are capable of being excellent at. We are meant to work but we don't have to hate the work we do. There's plenty of layers in this reality that need exactly what you offer.

Credits:  
Written, Performed, Co-Produced by Will Juergens  
Co-Produced, Mixed, Mastered by MAiWORLD  
Additional Drum Production by Synova  
Album Art created by Will Juergens and Synova.
